<lb n="0724a21"/><head type="no">No. 785</head>
<lb n="0724a22"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><title><note n="0724009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（佛說）＋得【明】，〔得道梯橙〕－【宮】</note><note n="0724009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔得道梯橙〕－【宮】，（佛說）＋得【明】</note><app n="0724009"><lem>得道梯<note n="0724010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">橙＝&CB00447;【三】</note><note n="0724010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">橙＝&CB00447;【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0724010"><lem>橙</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&CB00447;</rdg></app></lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">佛說得道梯橙</rdg></app>錫杖經</title></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0724a23"/>
<lb n="0724a24"/><byline type="Translator">失譯<note n="0724011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔人名〕－【宋】【元】【宮】</note><app n="0724011"><lem>人名</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>今附東晉錄</byline>
<lb n="0724a25"/><div1 type="jing"><p>爾時世尊告諸比丘。汝等皆應受持錫杖。所
<lb n="0724a26"/>以者何。過去諸佛執持錫杖。未來諸佛執持
<lb n="0724a27"/>錫杖。現在諸佛亦執<note n="0724012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">是＝持錫【三】【宮】</note><note n="0724012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">是＝持錫【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0724012"><lem>是</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">持錫</rdg></app>杖。如我今日成佛世
<lb n="0724a28"/>尊亦<note n="0724013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">執＋（持）【宮】＊</note><app n="0724013"><lem>執</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">執持</rdg></app>如是應持之杖。過去未來現在諸佛。
<lb n="0724a29"/>教諸弟子。亦<app type="＊" source="0724013"><lem>執</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">執持</rdg></app>錫杖。是以我今成佛世尊。
<pb ed="T" id="T17.0785.0724b" n="0724b"/>
<lb n="0724b01"/>如諸佛法。以教於汝。汝等今當受持錫杖。所
<lb n="0724b02"/>以者何。是錫杖者。名為智杖。亦名德杖。彰顯
<lb n="0724b03"/>聖智故。<note n="0724014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">名＝故曰【三】【宮】</note><note n="0724014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">名＝故曰【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0724014"><lem>名</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">故曰</rdg></app>智杖。行功德本故曰德杖。如是
<lb n="0724b04"/>杖者。聖人之表<note n="0724015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">式＝幟【元】【明】＊</note><app n="0724015"><lem>式</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">幟</rdg></app>。賢士之明記。趣道法之正
<lb n="0724b05"/>幢。建念義之志。是故汝等咸持如法。爾時尊
<lb n="0724b06"/>者迦葉從坐而起。整衣服偏袒右肩。合掌<note n="0724016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00566;＝胡【明】</note><note n="0724016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CI0004;＝胡跪【明】</note><app n="0724016"><lem>&CI0004;</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">胡跪</rdg></app>。
<lb n="0724b07"/>而白佛言。世尊。云何名錫杖。云何而受
<lb n="0724b08"/>持。唯然世尊。願<note n="0724017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">敷＝開【三】【宮】</note><note n="0724017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">敷＝開【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0724017"><lem>敷</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">開</rdg></app>演說。我<note n="0724018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">等奉＝一一【三】【宮】</note><note n="0724018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">等奉＝一一【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0724018"><lem>等奉</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">一一</rdg></app>行。佛告迦
<lb n="0724b09"/>葉。諦聽善<note n="0724019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">思＋（念）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0724019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">思＋（念）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0724019"><lem>思</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">思念</rdg></app>當為<note n="0724020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">汝說＝說之【三】【宮】</note><note n="0724020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">汝說＝說之【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0724020"><lem>汝說</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">說之</rdg></app>。所言錫杖者。錫者
<lb n="0724b10"/>輕也。依倚是杖。得除煩惱。出於三界。故曰輕
<lb n="0724b11"/>也。錫者明也。持杖之人。得智慧明。故曰明
<lb n="0724b12"/>也。錫言不迴。持是杖者。能出三<note n="0724021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">有＝界【三】【宮】</note><note n="0724021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">有＝界【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0724021"><lem>有</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">界</rdg></app>。不復染
<lb n="0724b13"/>著。故曰不迴。錫言<note n="0724022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">惺＝醒【元】【明】＊</note><app n="0724022"><lem>惺</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">醒</rdg></app>也。持是杖者。<app type="＊" source="0724022"><lem>惺</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">醒</rdg></app><note n="0724023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00322;＝悟【元】【明】</note><app n="0724023"><lem>&CB00322;</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">悟</rdg></app>
<lb n="0724b14"/>苦空三界結使。明了四諦十二緣起。故曰<app type="＊" source="0724022"><lem>惺</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">醒</rdg></app>
<lb n="0724b15"/>也。錫言不慢。持是杖者。<note n="0724024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">除斷＝斷除煩惱【三】【宮】</note><note n="0724024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">除斷＝斷除煩惱【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0724024"><lem>除斷</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">斷除煩惱</rdg></app>慢業。故曰不
<lb n="0724b16"/>慢。錫者言疏。持<note n="0724025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">此＝是【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0724025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">此＝是【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0724025"><lem>此</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">是</rdg></app>杖者。與五欲&CB00565;。斷貪愛
<lb n="0724b17"/>結。散壞<note n="0724026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">諸陰＝五陰【三】，諸五陰【宮】</note><note n="0724026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">諸陰＝五陰【宋】【元】【明】，＝諸五陰【宮】</note><app n="0724026"><lem>諸陰</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">五陰</rdg><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">諸五陰</rdg></app>。<note n="0724027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔遠〕－【宮】</note><app n="0724027"><lem>遠</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>離五<note n="0724028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">蓋＝苦【宮】</note><app n="0724028"><lem>蓋</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">苦</rdg></app>。志趣涅槃。疏<note n="0724029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">有＝者【三】【宮】</note><note n="0724029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">有＝者【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0724029"><lem>有</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">者</rdg></app>
<lb n="0724b18"/>為業。故曰&CB00565;也。錫言採取。持是杖者。採取
<lb n="0724b19"/>諸佛戒定慧寶。獲得解脫。故曰採取。錫者成
<lb n="0724b20"/>也。持是杖者。成就諸佛法藏。如說修行。不令
<lb n="0724b21"/>缺減。<note n="0724030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔悉具成就〕－【宮】</note><app n="0724030"><lem>悉具成就</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。故曰成也。佛告迦葉。如是
<lb n="0724b22"/>錫字。其義廣多。不可具陳。汝今<note n="0724031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">且當＝當知【三】</note><note n="0724031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">且當＝當知【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0724031"><lem>且當</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">當知</rdg></app>如是
<lb n="0724b23"/>受持。迦葉白<note n="0724032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔佛〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0724032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔佛〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0724032"><lem>佛</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>言。世尊。是錫杖者。其義<note n="0724033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">如是云何＝云何如是【宮】</note><app n="0724033"><lem>如
<lb n="0724b24"/>是。云何</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">云何如是</rdg></app>智杖。乃至建念義之志。唯然世尊。
<lb n="0724b25"/>願<note n="0724034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">為敷演＝敷演說【三】【宮】</note><note n="0724034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">為敷演＝敷演說【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0724034"><lem>為敷演</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">敷演說</rdg></app>。佛言。是錫杖者。為修智士。廣修
<lb n="0724b26"/>多聞。解世出世。分別善惡。有為無為。有漏
<lb n="0724b27"/>無漏。了<note n="0724035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">智＝知【三】【宮】</note><note n="0724035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">智＝知【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0724035"><lem>智</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">知</rdg></app>無礙。智慧成就。故曰智杖。為持
<lb n="0724b28"/>禁戒忍辱禪定。一心不亂。常修福業。無時懈
<lb n="0724b29"/><note n="0724036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">怠＝息【宮】</note><app n="0724036"><lem>怠</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">息</rdg></app>。如<note n="0724037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">救＝杖【宮】</note><app n="0724037"><lem>救</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">杖</rdg></app>頭然。故曰德杖。攝持是杖。如斯之
<pb ed="T" id="T17.0785.0724c" n="0724c"/>
<lb n="0724c01"/>人。內具十六行。謂四諦。苦集滅道。四等慈悲
<lb n="0724c02"/>喜捨。四禪初禪二禪三禪四禪。四無色定。
<lb n="0724c03"/>空處識處不用處非想非非想處。復具三十
<lb n="0724c04"/>七行。謂三十七助道法。於是法中。了了分別。
<lb n="0724c05"/><note n="0724038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">自身＝身自【三】【宮】</note><note n="0724038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">自身＝身自【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0724038"><lem>自身</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">身自</rdg></app>作證。不隨音聲。於是法中。而自<note n="0724039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">遨＝遊【三】【宮】</note><note n="0724039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">遨＝遊【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0724039"><lem>遨</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">遊</rdg></app>戲。
<lb n="0724c06"/>入空無相無願解脫門。自在無難。名之<note n="0724040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">為＝曰【三】【宮】</note><note n="0724040" resp="CBETA" type="mod">為＝曰【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0724040"><lem>為</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">曰</rdg></app>
<lb n="0724c07"/>聖。內有是德。外執錫杖。表<app type="＊" source="0724015"><lem>式</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">幟</rdg></app><app type="＊" source="0724025"><lem>此</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">是</rdg></app>人。必有聖
<lb n="0724c08"/>德。戒<note n="0724041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">定忍＝忍定【三】【宮】</note><note n="0724041" resp="CBETA" type="mod">定忍＝忍定【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0724041"><lem>定忍</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">忍定</rdg></app>慧。三明六通。及八解脫。皆悉
<lb n="0724c09"/>具有。以記此人。望表生敬。故曰聖人之表
<lb n="0724c10"/><note n="0724042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">式＝識【宋】【宮】，幟【元】【明】</note><note n="0724042" resp="CBETA" type="mod">式＝識【宋】【宮】，＝幟【元】【明】</note><app n="0724042"><lem>式</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【宮】" resp="Taisho">識</rdg><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">幟</rdg></app>也。賢士之明記者。內有智性。<note n="0724043" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔故〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0724043" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔故〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0724043"><lem>故</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>曰賢士
<lb n="0724c11"/>明記。此人內有智性。習功德本。於法增<note n="0724044" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（精）＋進【三】【宮】</note><note n="0724044" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（精）＋進【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0724044"><lem>進</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">精進</rdg></app>。
<lb n="0724c12"/>善<note n="0724045" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">心＝法【三】【宮】</note><note n="0724045" resp="CBETA" type="mod">心＝法【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0724045"><lem>心</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">法</rdg></app>成辦。故曰賢士明記。此人不久之間。
<lb n="0724c13"/>智慧成就。入無為處。寂然宴靜。涅槃安樂。第
<lb n="0724c14"/>一義道。故曰趣道之法幢。建念義之志者。
<lb n="0724c15"/>是杖有三<note n="0724046" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">鬲＝停【宋】，錞【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><note n="0724046" resp="CBETA" type="mod">鬲＝停【宋】，＝錞【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0724046"><lem>鬲</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">停</rdg><rdg wit="【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">錞</rdg></app>。見三<app type="＊" source="0724046"><lem>鬲</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】【宮】">錞</rdg></app>重。則念三塗苦惱。則
<lb n="0724c16"/>修戒定慧。念三災老病死。則除三毒貪瞋癡。
<lb n="0724c17"/>念三界之無常。則信重於三寶。除三惡。斷三
<lb n="0724c18"/>漏。淨三業。<note n="0724047" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">欲＝故【宮】</note><app n="0724047"><lem>欲</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">故</rdg></app>具三明。入<note n="0724048" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔三〕－【宮】</note><app n="0724048"><lem>三</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>解<note n="0724049" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">脫＋（也）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0724049" resp="CBETA" type="mod">脫＋（也）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0724049"><lem>脫</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">脫也</rdg></app>得三念
<lb n="0724c19"/>處。通三達智。故立三<app type="＊" source="0724046"><lem>鬲</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】【宮】">錞</rdg></app>。以相重也。復有四
<lb n="0724c20"/><note n="0724050" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">鉆＝楞【宋】，股【明】</note><note n="0724050" resp="CBETA" type="mod">鉆＝楞【宋】，＝股【明】</note><app n="0724050"><lem>鉆</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">楞</rdg><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">股</rdg></app>者。用斷四生。念四諦。修四等。入四禪。淨
<lb n="0724c21"/>四空。明四念處。堅<note n="0724051" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔四〕－【宮】</note><app n="0724051"><lem>四</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>正勤。得四神足。故立
<lb n="0724c22"/>四<note n="0724052" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">楞＝鈷【宋】【宮】，股【明】</note><note n="0724052" resp="CBETA" type="mod">楞＝鈷【宋】【宮】，＝股【明】</note><app n="0724052"><lem>楞</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【宮】" resp="Taisho">鈷</rdg><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">股</rdg></app>。通中<note n="0724053" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">鬲＝高【三】【宮】</note><note n="0724053" resp="CBETA" type="mod">鬲＝高【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0724053"><lem>鬲</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">高</rdg></app>五。用斷五道苦惱<note n="0724054" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">輪迴＝迴輪【三】【宮】</note><note n="0724054" resp="CBETA" type="mod">輪迴＝迴輪【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0724054"><lem>輪迴</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">迴輪</rdg></app>。修
<pb ed="T" id="T17.0785.0725a" n="0725a"/>
<lb n="0725a01"/>五根。具五力。除五蓋。散五陰。得五分法身。
<lb n="0725a02"/>故立五也。十二環者。用念十二因緣。通達無
<lb n="0725a03"/>礙。修行十二門禪<note n="0725001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">令＝念【三】【宮】</note><note n="0725001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">令＝念【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0725001"><lem>令</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">念</rdg></app>心無患。三重四<note n="0725002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">楞＝鈷【元】，股【明】，樓【宮】</note><note n="0725002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">楞＝鈷【元】，＝股【明】，＝樓【宮】</note><app n="0725002"><lem>楞</lem><rdg wit="【元】" resp="Taisho">鈷</rdg><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">股</rdg><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">樓</rdg></app>合
<lb n="0725a04"/>數成七。以念如來七覺意法。成就七聖財。通
<lb n="0725a05"/><app type="＊" source="0724046"><lem>鬲</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】【宮】">錞</rdg></app>鑽八用念八正道。得八解脫。除滅八難。
<lb n="0725a06"/>故用八也。略說錫杖其義如是。汝當<note n="0725003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">善＋（聽受）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0725003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">善＋（聽受）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0725003"><lem>善</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">善聽受</rdg></app>持。
<lb n="0725a07"/>迦葉白<note n="0725004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">佛＋（言）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0725004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">佛＋（言）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0725004"><lem>佛</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">佛言</rdg></app>。<note n="0725005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔如是〕－【宮】</note><app n="0725005"><lem>如是</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>世尊。如聖法教。</p>
<lb n="0725a08"/><p>爾時迦葉復白佛言。世尊。三世諸佛法同是
<lb n="0725a09"/>也。佛言。有杖是同。若用不同。或有<note n="0725006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">四＝二【三】【宮】</note><note n="0725006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">四＝二【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0725006"><lem>四</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">二</rdg></app><note n="0725007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">鈷＝股【明】＊</note><app n="0725007"><lem>鈷</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">股</rdg></app>。
<lb n="0725a10"/>或有<note n="0725008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">二＝四【三】【宮】</note><note n="0725008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">二＝四【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0725008"><lem>二</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">四</rdg></app><app type="＊" source="0725007"><lem>鈷</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">股</rdg></app>。環數無別。但我今日四<app type="＊" source="0725007"><lem>鈷</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">股</rdg></app>十二
<lb n="0725a11"/>環用是之教。二<app type="＊" source="0725007"><lem>鈷</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">股</rdg></app>者迦葉如來<note n="0725009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">之所制立＝所制立也【三】【宮】</note><note n="0725009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">之所制立＝所制立也【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0725009"><lem>之所制立</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">所制立也</rdg></app>。
<lb n="0725a12"/>令諸眾生記念二諦。世諦第一義諦。<note n="0725010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔以立其義〕－【宮】</note><app n="0725010"><lem>以立
<lb n="0725a13"/>其義</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。爾時世尊。說<app type="＊" source="0724025"><lem>此</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">是</rdg></app>法已。尊者迦葉。千二
<lb n="0725a14"/>百眾。及諸大會。皆悉歡喜。頂戴奉行◎<note n="0725011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">於此分經【元】【明】，得道梯&CB00447;錫杖經（經末題）【元】，佛說得道梯&CB00447;錫杖經（經末題）【明】，佛說持錫杖法（經首題）【元】，持錫杖法（經首題）【明】</note><note n="0725011" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><todo type="a"/>於此分經【元】【明】，得道梯&CB00447;錫杖經（經末題）【元】，佛說得道梯&CB00447;錫杖經（經末題）【明】，佛說持錫杖法（經首題）【元】，持錫杖法（經首題）【明】</note>。</p>
<lb n="0725a15"/><p>◎<note n="0725012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">於此分經【元】【明】，得道梯&CB00447;錫杖經（經末題）【元】，佛說得道梯&CB00447;錫杖經（經末題）【明】，佛說持錫杖法（經首題）【元】，持錫杖法（經首題）【明】。凡體…正覺三百六十五字∞持錫…奉行三百五十五字【三】</note><note n="0725012" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><todo type="a"/>於此分經【元】【明】，得道梯&CB00447;錫杖經（經末題）【元】，佛說得道梯&CB00447;錫杖經（經末題）【明】，佛說持錫杖法（經首題）【元】，持錫杖法（經首題）【明】。凡體…正覺三百六十五字∞持錫…奉行三百五十五字【宋】【元】【明】</note>凡體法。上臺法天。下臺法地。四<note n="0725013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">支＝枝【三】【宮】</note><note n="0725013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">支＝枝【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0725013"><lem>支</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">枝</rdg></app>法四
<lb n="0725a16"/>天王。十二環法十二因緣。<note n="0725014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">包＝苞【宮】</note><app n="0725014"><lem>包</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">苞</rdg></app>含天地人天上
<lb n="0725a17"/>下。無不斯盡。凡發<note n="0725015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">慈＋（心）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0725015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">慈＋（心）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0725015"><lem>慈</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">慈心</rdg></app>。廣生萬行<note n="0725016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">物＝勿【三】【宮】</note><note n="0725016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">物＝勿【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0725016"><lem>物</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">勿</rdg></app>不准
<lb n="0725a18"/>此。已起善本。持<note n="0725017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">此杖法＝杖法此【三】【宮】</note><note n="0725017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">此杖法＝杖法此【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0725017"><lem>此杖法</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">杖法此</rdg></app>。齎天<note n="0725018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">挾＝俠【宋】【元】【宮】</note><note n="0725018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">挾＝俠【宋】【元】【宮】<app><lem resp="CBETA.say">＊</lem><rdg wit="【大】"></rdg></app></note><app n="0725018"><lem>挾</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【宮】" resp="Taisho">俠</rdg></app>地。著左&CB00169;
<lb n="0725a19"/>下。以小指<note n="0725019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">句＝拘【三】【宮】</note><note n="0725019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">句＝拘【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0725019"><lem>句</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">拘</rdg></app>之。使兩頭平正。不令高下。鳴
<lb n="0725a20"/>則常鳴。不令聲絕。<note n="0725020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔其聲〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0725020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔其聲〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0725020"><lem>其聲</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>均細調和。琩洐Y
<lb n="0725a21"/>初。若初無聲訖。一行處不令有聲。若初有聲
<lb n="0725a22"/>訖。一行處常令有聲。亦<note n="0725021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">使＝令【三】【宮】</note><note n="0725021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">使＝令【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0725021"><lem>使</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">令</rdg></app>&CB00308;細一等不得。
<lb n="0725a23"/>或&CB00308;或細。僧<note n="0725022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">置＝著【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0725022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">置＝著【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0725022"><lem>置</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">著</rdg></app>左<note n="0725023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">足＋（上）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0725023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">足＋（上）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0725023"><lem>足</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">足上</rdg></app>。尼<app type="＊" source="0725022"><lem>置</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">著</rdg></app>右足。不得著
<lb n="0725a24"/>地。若檀越<note n="0725024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔不〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0725024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔不〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0725024"><lem>不</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>出。近至三家。遠滿七家。若不
<lb n="0725a25"/>得更不容多過。若過非行者法。若限內得食。
<lb n="0725a26"/>持杖懸之樹上。勿令著地。若無樹著地。<note n="0725025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">就地平處一＝平處【三】【宮】</note><note n="0725025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">就地平處一＝平處【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0725025"><lem>就
<lb n="0725a27"/>地平處<note n="0725026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔一〕－【宮】</note><app n="0725026"><lem>一</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">平處</rdg></app>不令傾側。眠時<note n="0725027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔安〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0725027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔安〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0725027"><lem>安</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>杖與身相順。
<lb n="0725a28"/>置之床後。正與身齊。不令前&CB00230;。持行路止息
<lb n="0725a29"/>時。頭常向日。勿令倒逆違背。持此杖即持佛
<pb ed="T" id="T17.0785.0725b" n="0725b"/>
<lb n="0725b01"/>身。萬行盡在其中。謂持天<app type="＊" source="0725018"><lem>挾</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【宮】">俠</rdg></app>地。并觀十二
<lb n="0725b02"/>因緣。為護<note n="0725028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">身＋（亦護）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0725028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">身＋（亦護）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0725028"><lem>身</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">身亦護</rdg></app>。一切如其傾側。一切萬物皆
<lb n="0725b03"/>亦傾側。如其平正。一切含生。皆令安隱無為。
<lb n="0725b04"/>若下臺著地之時。令三塗眾生苦劇踰增。若
<lb n="0725b05"/>不著地。令三塗眾生因之得拔。如其顛倒。則
<lb n="0725b06"/>逆世界。亦令行者其心迷亂。若能<note n="0725029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">順＝慎【三】【宮】</note><note n="0725029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">順＝慎【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0725029"><lem>順</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">慎</rdg></app>持。彼
<lb n="0725b07"/>此俱<note n="0725030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">利＋（矣）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0725030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">利＋（矣）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0725030"><lem>利</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">利矣</rdg></app>若<note n="0725031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔如〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0725031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔如〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0725031"><lem>如</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>是持。具現得威儀<note n="0725032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔出〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0725032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔出〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0725032"><lem>出</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>入護助。
<lb n="0725b08"/>後得獲果。速成正覺。</p>
<lb n="0725b09"/><p>◎<note n="0725033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">凡體…正覺三百六十五字∞持錫…奉行三百五十五字【三】，〔持錫…奉行〕三百五十五字－【宮】</note><note n="0725033" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><todo type="a"/>凡體…正覺三百六十五字∞持錫…奉行三百五十五字【宋】【元】【明】，〔持錫…奉行〕三百五十五字－【宮】</note>持錫杖威儀法。有二十五事。持錫杖十事
<lb n="0725b10"/>法。一者為地有蟲故。二者為年朽老故。三
<lb n="0725b11"/>者為分越故。四者不得手持而前&CB00230;。五者不
<lb n="0725b12"/>得擔杖著肩上。六者不得橫著肩<note n="0725034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔上〕－【三】</note><note n="0725034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔上〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0725034"><lem>上</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>手垂兩
<lb n="0725b13"/>頭。七者出入見佛像不聽有聲。八者杖不得
<lb n="0725b14"/>入眾。九者不得妄持至舍後。十者<note n="0725035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">杖過中不＝不得持杖過中【三】</note><note n="0725035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">杖過中不＝不得持杖過中【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0725035"><lem>杖過中不</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">不得持杖過中</rdg></app>
<lb n="0725b15"/>出。復有五事。一者遠請行宿過中得出。二者
<lb n="0725b16"/>至病瘦家過中得出。三者送過世者過中得
<lb n="0725b17"/>出。四者外道請者過中得出。五者不得將杖
<lb n="0725b18"/>指人畫地作字。復有五事。一者三師俱出不
<lb n="0725b19"/>得持杖自隨。二者四人共行除上座不得普
<lb n="0725b20"/>持。三者到檀越門好正威儀。四者入檀越門
<lb n="0725b21"/>三抖擻三反不出從至餘家。五者檀越出應
<lb n="0725b22"/>持杖著左肘中央。</p>
<lb n="0725b23"/><p>復有五事。一者杖琣b己房中不得離身。二
<lb n="0725b24"/>者不聽下頭著地。三者不聽杖許生衣。四者
<lb n="0725b25"/>日日須好磨拭。五者杖欲出時當從沙彌邊
<lb n="0725b26"/>受。若無沙彌白衣亦得。</p>
<lb n="0725b27"/><lg><l>錫杖四鈷應四諦</l><l>環應十二因緣</l>
<lb n="0725b28"/><l>中召明中道義</l><l>上頭應須彌頂</l>
<lb n="0725b29"/><l>第二應須彌山</l><l>中央木應於空</l>
<pb ed="T" id="T17.0785.0725c" n="0725c"/>
<lb n="0725c01"/><l>下錯應須彌根</l></lg>
<lb n="0725c02"/><p>沙門之法。解空得道。執此<note n="0725036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">惺&CB00896;＝醒悟【元】【明】，&CB13541;&CB00896;【宋】</note><note n="0725036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">惺&CB00896;＝醒悟【元】【明】，＝&CB13541;&CB00896;【宋】</note><app n="0725036"><lem>惺&CB00896;</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">醒悟</rdg><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">&CB13541;&CB00896;</rdg></app>。世間一切
<lb n="0725c03"/>眾生。諸比丘等至心奉行。</p></div1>
<lb n="0725c04"/><juan fun="close" n="001"><jhead><title><note n="0725037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔得道梯橙錫杖經〕－【元】【明】，〔得道梯橙〕－【宮】</note><app n="0725037"><lem>得道梯橙錫杖經</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">錫杖經</rdg></app></title></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0725c05"/>
<lb n="0725c06"/><div1 type="W"><mulu type="附文" level="1" n="2" label="又持錫杖法"/><head>◎<note n="0725038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">又持錫杖法麗本宋本宮本無今依明本採錄與元本對挍，又＝佛說【元】</note><app n="0725038"><lem>又</lem><rdg wit="【元】" resp="Taisho">佛說</rdg></app><note n="0725038" place="foot" type="rest">又持錫杖法麗本宋本宮本無今依明本採錄與元本對挍</note>持錫杖法<note place="inline">依天竺藏經重出使後人看閱知其源流也</note></head>
<lb n="0725c07"/>
<lb n="0725c08"/><p>錫杖有二十五事威儀。持錫杖有二十五
<lb n="0725c09"/>事者。一者為蛇蟲故。二者為年老故。三者
<lb n="0725c10"/>為分衛故。四者為出入見佛像不得使頭
<lb n="0725c11"/>有聲。五者不得持杖入眾。六者中後不得
<lb n="0725c12"/>復杖出。七者不得擔著肩上以手懸兩頭。
<lb n="0725c13"/>八者不得橫著膝上以懸兩頭。九者不得
<lb n="0725c14"/>手掉前後。十者不得持至舍後。十一者不
<lb n="0725c15"/>得復持在三師前後。已杖出不得復杖隨。
<lb n="0725c16"/>十二者若四人俱行。一人已持。不得復持
<lb n="0725c17"/>隨。十三者若至檀越家。不得捨杖離身。
<lb n="0725c18"/>十四者至人門戶時。當三抖擻不出應當
<lb n="0725c19"/>更至餘家。十五者主人出應當杖著左肘
<lb n="0725c20"/>挾之。十六者若至室中。不得使著地。十
<lb n="0725c21"/>七者當持自近臥床。十八者當數取拭之。
<lb n="0725c22"/>十九者不使頭有生。二十者欲行當從沙
<lb n="0725c23"/>彌若白衣受。二十一者至病人家宿應得
<lb n="0725c24"/>暮杖。二十二者欲遠送過去者應得暮杖。
<pb ed="T" id="T17.0785.0726a" n="0726a"/>
<lb n="0726a01"/>二十三者遠請行宿應得暮杖。二十四者
<lb n="0726a02"/>遠迎來者應得暮杖。二十五者常當自近
<lb n="0726a03"/>不得指人若畫地作字。</p>
<lb n="0726a04"/><p><note n="0726001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔持錫杖法〕－【元】</note><app n="0726001"><lem>持錫杖法</lem><rdg wit="【元】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></p></div1>
